Pin Diagram:

Component	Arduino Pin
HC-SR04 Trig	9
HC-SR04 Echo	10
Servo MG90S	6
LED	3
Power Connections:

HC-SR04 VCC → 5V

HC-SR04 GND → GND

Servo VCC → 5V

Servo GND → GND

LED Anode (+) → Digital Pin 3 (with 220Ω resistor)

LED Cathode (-) → GND

MG90S Servo 3-Pin Color Code & Connections
Wire Color	Function	Arduino Connection
Brown	GND (Ground)	GND
Red	VCC (Power +5V)	5V
Orange	Signal (PWM)	Digital Pin 6
